detail.name: Time Rewound
detail.effect: [Activate Battle][Opponent's Turn] Choose your Leader or up to 1 of your Battle Cards and it gets +20000 power for the battle. Then, choose up to 1 of your Battle Cards and switch it to Active Mode.
